column1: Distributor and Dealer Price List w.e.f. 10th Febraury'2025
Prices Are Inclusive Of IGST/CGST/SGST as applicable.
Apart from MRP, all other prices mentioned above are exclusive of IGST/CGST/SGST and as applicable.
All payments should be by way of RTGS / DD / CHEQUE drawn on any nationalised bank.
This pricelist supersedes any /or all earlier communicated pricelist for these products.
Prices are subject to revision with prior intimation. Prices ruling at the time of delivery shall apply.
For every container order 25% advance against the Proforma to be paid and balance amount to be paid  in 30days from the date of Invoice raised.
4% Cash Discount for full payment against Proforma Invoice (on 75% of the amount)
For all container orders transport cost will be at actuals from the Ex depo Bengaluru.
Company shall not be responsible for any shortages, damages or loss in transit from VOX warehouse or Distributor warehouse.
